@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : scheduleFlight(routeId, aircraftRegistration, scheduledDateTime)
activate System

note right of System: The system validates the route is active,\nverifies aircraft range requirements,\nchecks aircraft availability (no conflicts),\nand creates the scheduled flight.

System --> ATCC : informs operation success and returns created scheduled flight
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
